resources.string:
To enable push notifications, you must enter the following URL in the 'SMS URL Callback' field of the SMS settings for your DID on the VoIP.ms portal:

http://voipmssms-kourlas.rhcloud.com/sms_callback?did={DID}

Note that the developer's Google Cloud Messaging server will store your DID to forward callbacks from VoIP.ms to your device. See Help for more details.
